e good. (although at 58th+ level the jade mace hits for more damage on high ac mobs)  Aggro is really the factor here. Can the Frosty be workable in the mainhand as a taunter?<br><br>I could dig up a Jade Mace easily, but not sure if I could get anything better than that. Even if the Frosty works fine for mainhand, should I ditch the venomous and get a better offhand?? I love the ac, but the proc is crap for Aggro (85 dd) and the dam/delay ratio isn't that great.<br><br>Thoughts/comments?<br><br>Sumarr Shadowcleaver <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 286<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/4/02 12:08:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1746.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Weapon selection...</span><hr size=1> JM mainhand and frosty off hand is a pretty nice combo.<br><br>Start saving for a Defiance or Wavecrasher to replace the JM. <p><div align="center" style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial"><img src="http://www.bfdesigns.net/eq/wandor_sig.jpg"><br><a target="_blank" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6103"><b>Wandor's profile</b></a> | <a target="_blank" href="http://www.exarch.net/"><b>Fusion of Flame</b></a> | <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6102" target="_blank"><b>Moordian's profile</b></a></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valig